## LICENSE ACCEPTANCE

Acceptance of this License (EULA) occurs through **two linked mechanisms**:

1. **Local contract with the Contributor.** The customer enters into a purchase
   or license agreement in their jurisdiction with an **Authorized Contributor**.
   **Mandatory appendices** to that contract are this LICENSE and
   [service-terms.md](docs.en/service-terms.md) (or Contributor-localized versions
   approved by the copyright holder). The local contract governs commercial terms:
   price, payment, taxes, refunds, claims, governing law, and jurisdiction. It
   **may not** restrict the copyright holder’s rights below this License,
   **except** where applicable law explicitly improves the customer’s position.

2. **Receipt of the license token.** Crediting a **license token** to the
   customer’s wallet address on **Sepolia** (see service-terms) **constitutes
   acceptance** of this License with the **copyright holder** (Author or
   successor under “Succession and Assignment”). Date, wallet address, and token amount are recorded
   on-chain.

Both mechanisms **complement each other**: the local contract frames the sale
 with the seller in the customer’s country; token receipt confirms the EULA with
 the copyright holder and binds the license to the wallet.

